            <h2>Accessibility in HTML5</h2>
            <p>Accessibility ensures that web content is usable by everyone, including people with disabilities. 
               HTML5 introduces landmarks like <code>&lt;header&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code>, <code>&lt;main&gt;</code>, and <code>&lt;footer&gt;</code> 
               that help screen readers understand page structure.</p>
        </section>

